snippet.title: GAMEPLAY FNF IDOL | Friday Night Funkin
snippet.description:
Mod based on the anime Oshi no ko

This mod contain some of oshi no ko songs from the anime and maybe some cover do by other user

(All credits of the covers go to respective owner).

Original song: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZRtdQ81jPUQ&t=0s https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=shEwhe3sDpo
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A9ZC_917IvU (Star T Rain, Sing Wa B and Idol).

Thanks for all your support and patience, now LET'S HAVE SOME FUN.

MOD LINK https://gamebanana.com/mods/454682
